room_title: Escape room "Infection" by Unity Escape Rooms in Redlands
room_address: 2015 W Park Ave Suite 2B Redlands, CA 92373
room_description: Since 2005 Unity Labs has worked tirelessly to protect you from the world’s deadliest pathogens. Recently congress approved funding for a new high containment lab complex but before the work can start we need to clean out the old labs. As part of the CDC’s emergency response team it’s your job to clean out the labs in a safe manner making sure no virus’ are released into the ventilation system. Dr. Grant will brief you when you arrive. Good luck and try not to get infected…
